

Создай в корне проекта файл **`.gitignore`** (важно с точкой в начале!):

```gitignore
# Built application files
*.apk
*.ap_
*.aab

# Files for the ART/Dalvik VM
*.dex

# Java class files
*.class

# Generated files
bin/
gen/
out/

# Gradle files
.gradle/
build/

# Local configuration file
local.properties

# Android Studio
*.iml
.idea/
.navigation/
captures/

# OS-specific files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# Keystore files
*.jks
*.keystore

# External native build folder
.externalNativeBuild/
.cxx/

# Google Services
google-services.json
